"automatically with no setup required. Instagram and Facebook require a free "
"Meta Developer App because Meta deprecated anonymous oEmbed access in "
"October 2020."
msgstr ""
"YouTube, Vimeo, TikTok, Twitter/X, Spotify, SoundCloud en TED Talks worden "
"automatisch ingebed zonder vereiste instelling. Instagram en Facebook "
"vereisen een gratis Meta Developer App omdat Meta anonieme oEmbed-toegang "
"in oktober 2020 heeft afgeschaft."

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1045
msgid "Facebook App ID"
msgstr "Facebook-app-ID"

#: includes/admin/views/settings.php:1048
